## Color Palette

### Primary Gradient
- `from-cyan-400` → `via-blue-500` → `to-blue-600`
- Use for main background: `bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 via-blue-500 to-blue-600`

### Glass Morphism
- Primary: `bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20`
- Secondary: `bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30`
- Tertiary: `bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/40`

### Status Colors
- Success: `#22C55E` (green-500)
- Warning: `#F59E0B` (orange-500)
- Critical: `#EF4444` (red-500)
- Info: `#22D3EE` (cyan-400)

### Text Colors
- Primary: `text-white` (100% opacity)
- Secondary: `text-white/90`
- Tertiary: `text-white/80`
- Muted: `text-white/70`

