## Typography Rules

- **Don't use Tailwind font-size, font-weight, or line-height classes** unless specifically requested
- Let default HTML element typography apply
- Always add `drop-shadow` or `drop-shadow-lg` to white text over gradients
- Use opacity variants for text hierarchy: `text-white/90`, `text-white/80`, `text-white/70`

