## Implementation Notes

1. Always use glass morphism for cards over gradient backgrounds
2. Add text shadows to white text for readability
3. Use appropriate opacity levels for visual hierarchy
4. Maintain consistent spacing (p-4, p-6, gap-3, gap-6)
5. Use backdrop-blur for glass effects
6. Apply smooth transitions (duration-300) for interactive elements

